sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User (Browser)
    participant UI as Next.js UI
    participant MW as Middleware
    participant SA as Server Action
    participant AUTH as getCaller() / Supabase
    participant Q as queries.ts / Prisma
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant CACHE as Next.js Cache

    U->>UI: Click "Create Leave"
    UI->>SA: executeServerMutation('leave.create', input)
    SA->>MW: request passes through
    SA->>AUTH: resolve caller + role
    AUTH-->>SA: Caller {id, isAdmin, branchId}
    alt Unauthorized
        SA-->>UI: MutationError(UNAUTHORIZED)
    else Authorized
        SA->>Q: prisma.leaveRequest.create(...)
        Q->>DB: INSERT
        DB-->>Q: row
        Q-->>SA: created record
        SA->>CACHE: revalidateForPath('leave')
        SA-->>UI: result
        UI->>CACHE: router.refresh()
        CACHE-->>UI: fresh data
    end

    Note over SA,DB: All mutations go through one router →<br/>auth, revalidate, typed errors, Sentry
